headline: ASUS Launches Exclusive Early Black Friday Offers
summary: Save up to C$750 and enjoy up to 50% off laptops, desktops, and accessories starting November 21KEY POINTS Start saving early: Early Black Friday deals begin November 21, with additional discounts launching on Black Friday and Cyber Monday.Massive holiday savings: Get up to C$750 off and up to 50% off ASUS laptops, desktops, Chromebooks, and more.Shop at your favorite retailers: Deals available at Amazon, ASUS Store, Best Buy, Canada Computers, Costco, London Drugs, Staples, Walmart, and more.
